{"tid":1060024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★曾到深圳29歲港男染腦膜炎雙球菌　要入ICU----這病經由飛沫傳播","createTime":"2019-03-13T13:23:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T13:39:12.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"377a80b08201985034aeedfa21972a9965cffcb5","tid":1060024,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T13:23:10.000Z","msg":"衞生防護中心正調查一宗侵入性腦膜炎雙球菌感染個案，<span style=\"color: red;\">這病經由直接接觸帶菌者或受感染者的飛沫而傳播</span>。病者是過往健康良好的29歲香港男子，自本月9日起出現發燒、嘔吐、頭痛和頸痛等病徵。他於11日入住明愛醫院，同日被轉往深切治療部接受治療，臨床診斷為敗血性休克，病人現時情況穩定。病人的血液樣本經化驗後，證實對腦膜炎雙球菌呈陽性反應。 <br />\n<br />\n初步調查顯示，病人於潛伏期內曾前往深圳。他的家居接觸者至今沒有出現病徵。衞生防護中心解釋，腦膜炎雙球菌感染由腦膜炎雙球菌所引起，主要經由直接接觸帶菌者的呼吸道分泌物(包括口鼻分泌物)而傳播。潛伏期由2至10日，一般為3至4日。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190313/bkn-20190313190515333-0313_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190313%2Fbkn-20190313190515333-0313_00822_001.html&d=ctOUxKLv%2B9zBCrzB%2FMEnrZzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=77d919cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190313/bkn-20190313190515333-0313_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"df4fc8149c58ef228e4cabb2864ebe4c8acc527f","tid":1060024,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T13:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"506876d1f6aa7d4d3390fb4490f3140c13454c27","tid":1060024,"uid":20554,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T13:24:32.000Z","msg":"雞蟲？"},{"pid":"9764b9bbb66a4c7fff7af009705ad610112d09e7","tid":1060024,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T13:36:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb14e5317fa09b549f9f1d6c22d5d838e2c9f78c","tid":1060024,"uid":199120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T13:39:12.000Z","msg":"環保吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}